#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "Översikt"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <group choice=\"opt\" rep=\"repeat"
"\"><replaceable class=\"option\">OPTIONS</replaceable></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <group choice=\"opt\" rep=\"repeat"
"\"><replaceable class=\"option\">VÄLJARE</replaceable></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beskrivning"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> builds binary cache of the data stored in "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> and &MIME; type <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal> files that the KService framework uses to find "
"plugins, applications and other services."
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> skapar en binär cache av data lagrad i "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal>- och &MIME;-typ <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal>-filer som KService ramverk använder för att "
"hitta insticksprogram, program och andra tjänster."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The KService library uses this database to efficiently provide the "
"information requested of it."
msgstr ""
"KService-biblioteket använder databasen för att tillhandahålla informationen "
"som begärs av det på ett effektivt sätt."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Users do not normally need to run this application directly; KService will "
"run it if necessary, when any of the files whose data is cached are changed."
msgstr ""
"Användare behöver normalt inte köra programmet direkt: KService körs vid "
"behov, så fort någon av filerna vars data är lagrad ändras."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Väljare"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "--global"
msgstr "--global"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ignores any user-set files (in <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</varname>). This is "
"currently only supported on &UNIX; systems."
msgstr ""
"Ignorerar eventuella användarangivna filer (i <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</"
"varname>). Det stöds för närvarande bara på &UNIX;-system."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "--noincremental"
msgstr "--noincremental"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rather than using the existing cache and only updating the information that "
"has changed or been added, start with an empty cache. Ignored if <option>--"
"global</option> is set."
msgstr ""
"Starta med en tom cache istället för att använda den befintliga cachen och "
"bara uppdatera informationen som har ändrats eller lagts till. Ignoreras om "
"<option>--global</option> anges."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "--menutest"
msgstr "--menutest"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Test the generation of the application menu database. Does not actually "
"build the cache."
msgstr ""
"Prova generering av databasen för programmenyn. Skapar i själva verket inte "
"cachen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "--testmode"
msgstr "--testmode"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the QStandardPaths \"test mode\" to avoid interfering with user data. "
"This is intended for use with unit tests."
msgstr ""
"Använder 'provläge' i QStandardPaths för att undvika att påverka "
"användardata. Det är avsett att användas med enhetsutprovning."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "--track <replaceable>menu-id</replaceable>"
msgstr "--track <replaceable>meny-id</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track a menu ID for debugging."
msgstr "Spåra en menyidentifikation i felsökningssyfte."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "--author"
msgstr "--author"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show author information."
msgstr "Visa information om upphovsman."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "--license"
msgstr "--license"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show license information."
msgstr "Visa licensinformation."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help"
msgstr "-h, --help"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a brief help text."
msgstr "Visa en kortfattad hjälptext."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v , --version"
msgstr "-v , --version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
