#, no-c-format
msgid "Bugs"
msgstr "Fel"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please use <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org\">&kde;'s bugtracker</ulink> to "
